comments: Very smart teacher!!!! I wish there were more teachers like him at Logan. He knows his material!!!! Genious!!!! I only got a C+ in his classes (Physio I, II, III) but i learned more than in any other classes. Has an accent, but he is fantastic!!!! Very funny at times, but great job!!! Go MAMA BEAR!!!!!

Tough but fair. Genuinely cares that you grasp the concepts. Is very accessible to students and always willing to take extra time to explain things. Not an easy class...you will have to work hard for your grade. What seem to be straight forward concepts are at times twisted into obtuse exam questions. Go review your test after exams. It will help
Great teacher, demands alot, and you have to work to get your grade.
